<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chung Pathien guotsa hinkhuo phat chawmcha hi mangphan,
 Tui banga a luon mang kal hin;
 Paucham in ngen hitiu ie, kumsawt hinna lul pen,
 Zang taka hinkhuo mat theih na'n.

[V2]
 Ka damsung, ka damlai ni simdan ei sinsak in,
 Chitna lunggil neihlawh hiel nan;
 Na deih bang ka hawl ua hihdan ka thiem na'ng un,
 Vangpiekna tincheng ei vukin.

[V3]
 2. Damsung phat a bei paia, pak bang a vuoi paia,
 Nunnuom a I nuih lai niu haw;
 Lungkham ni gui khaubanga sau ding hi I gelin,
 Lungmuonna Pa kawmah ngenin.

[V4]
 3. Zang taka chieh theihna din' sietlei gam hak mah leh,
 Pathien su kipak in um in;
 Na lautha thangvan sangah kumsawt hin a channan,
 Samin, A sakmin ni chengin.</lyrics>
<title>I Damlai Niu</title>
<author>P.S. Chawngthu</author>
<hymn_number>154</hymn_number>
</song>